@baseUrl = http://localhost:5500
@clerkToken = <pegar_token_de_sesion_clerk>

### Registrar coach
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "COACH",
  "name": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan@example.com"
}

### Registrar estudiante (después de aceptar invitación Clerk)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Authorization: Bearer {{clerkToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "STUDENT",
  "name": "María García",
  "email": "maria@example.com"
}
